{"tid":521702,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"(銀行）想行Sales 條路","createTime":"2018-01-06T19:29:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-24T03:23:01.000Z","uid":165814,"like":4,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"7f3d2000d81fa7374bd141972d802f04b972b9d9","tid":521702,"uid":165814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T19:29:39.000Z","msg":"自己學歷唔係特別好，一般垃圾BBA Ugrad，打算轉行行RM 條路<br />\n除左考牌， 帶雙親返工之外<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，各位巴打有無意見可以比下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想了解多d retail 同 crop 既入行 / 工作上既分<br />\n<br />\n真係入行，又應該選擇邊類型既銀行呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n麻煩晒咁多位巴打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0747a4096fdd984762f16a3540d46ea6455b24b","tid":521702,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T20:42:58.000Z","msg":"retail banking會唔會好快收皮<br />\n<br />\n後生搵錢老左俾人炒因為無技能無樣sell人已經"},{"pid":"5b699934265ee65c8610617aaf311668a95b3d83","tid":521702,"uid":165814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d0747a4096fdd984762f16a3540d46ea6455b24b","tid":521702,"uid":107755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-06T20:42:58.000Z","msg":"retail banking會唔會好快收皮<br />\n<br />\n後生搵錢老左俾人炒因為無技能無樣sell人已經"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T03:32:28.000Z","msg":"我都明白既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但係感覺上做crop 好似相對難入行，同埋向上既機會都會比較慢？<br />\n<br />\n就咁睇retail 既流失率高得好緊要，轉工既機會多d，當然都知道佢既壓力程度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> , 如果做幾年既retail 要internal 轉其他post 又有無呢個玩法呢<br />\n<br />\n還是巴打都會覺得直接走crop 會平穩易行d <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"252bef879b4b23301df23090167bed0249473143","tid":521702,"uid":165814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-07T07:31:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/fac